==English==
===Transitive verb===
'''prescribe''' ([[prescribes]], [[prescribed]], [[prescribing]])

#To [[order]] (a [[drug]] or [[medical]] [[device]]) for use by a particular [[patient]].
#To [[specify]] as a required [[procedure]] or [[ritual]].

